import {css} from "emotion";
 
import styleMemoize from "../../../utils/style-memoize";
import getButtonVars from "./button.var";
// import buttonStyle from "./button.style";
import {solidifyOpacity,unitMath} from "../../../utils/css-utils";
 
import iconOnlyButton from "./types/icon-only-button.style";
import labeledIconButton from "./types/labeled-icon-button.style";
import compactButtons from "./types/compact-buttons.style";
import basicButton from "./types/basic-button.style";
import basicInvertedButton from "./types/basic-inverted-button.style";
 
export default styleMemoize(function({siteOverrides,overrides} = {}) {
 
  const buttonVars = getButtonVars({siteOverrides,overrides});
  const buttonClass = "aek-button";
 
  const {
    horizontalMargin,
    verticalMargin,
    borderRadius,
    groupBoxShadow,
    groupButtonOffset,
    groupButtonBoxShadow,
    verticalBoxShadow,
    verticalGroupOffset,
    getSize,
    basicBorderSize,
    borderColor,
    invertedGroupButtonOffset,
    invertedVerticalGroupButtonOffset,
    selectedBorderColor,
    orText,
    orGap,
    orHeight,
    orZIndex,
    orCircleSize,
    orLineHeight,
    orBoxShadow,
    orVerticalOffset,
    orHorizontalOffset,
    orBackgroundColor,
    orTextShadow,
    orTextStyle,
    orTextWeight,
    orTextColor,
    circularRadius,
  } = buttonVars;
 
  const {compactButton,compactIconButton,compactLabeledIconButton} = compactButtons(buttonVars);
 
  const group = css`
    label: button-group;
 
    & {
      display: inline-flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      vertical-align: baseline;
      margin: ${verticalMargin} ${horizontalMargin} 0em 0em;
    & {
      font-size: 1em;
    }
    &:not(.basic):not(.inverted) {
      box-shadow: ${groupBoxShadow};
    }
 
    /* Clearfix */
    &:after {
      content: ".";
      display: block;
      height: 0;
      clear: both;
      visibility: hidden;
      font-size: 0em;
    }
 
    /* Standard Group */
    & .${buttonClass} {
      flex: 1 0 auto;
      margin: 0em;
      border-radius: 0em;
      margin: ${groupButtonOffset};
    }
    &:not(.basic):not(.inverted) > .${buttonClass}:not(.basic):not(.inverted) {
      box-shadow: ${groupButtonBoxShadow};
    }
 
    & .${buttonClass}:first-child {
      border-left: none;
      margin-left: 0em;
      border-top-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
      border-bottom-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
    }
    & .${buttonClass}:last-child {
      border-top-right-radius: ${borderRadius};
      border-bottom-right-radius: ${borderRadius};
    }
 
    /* Vertical  Style */
    &.vertical {
      display: inline-flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    &.vertical .${buttonClass} {
      display: block;
      float: none;
      width: 100%;
      margin: ${verticalGroupOffset};
      box-shadow: ${verticalBoxShadow};
      border-radius: 0em;
    }
    &.vertical .${buttonClass}:first-child {
      border-top-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
      border-top-right-radius: ${borderRadius};
    }
    &.vertical .${buttonClass}:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0px;
      border-bottom-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
      border-bottom-right-radius: ${borderRadius};
    }
    &.vertical .${buttonClass}:only-child {
      border-radius: ${borderRadius};
    }
 
 
    &.divided:not(.vertical):not(.basic) > .${buttonClass} {
      margin-right:1px;
      &:last-child {
        margin-right:0;
      }
    }
    &.divided.vertical:not(.basic) > .${buttonClass} {
      margin-bottom:1px;
      &:last-child {
        margin-bottom:0;
      }
    }
    &.fluid:not(.vertical) > .${buttonClass} {
      flex: 1 0 0;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
 
    /*--------------
        Icon Only
    ---------------*/
 
    &.icon .${buttonClass} {
      ${iconOnlyButton(buttonVars)}
    }
 
    /*--------------
      Labeled Icon
    ---------------*/
 
    &.labeled .${buttonClass} {
      ${labeledIconButton(buttonVars)}
    }
 
    &.labeled.icon .${buttonClass} > .icon {
      border-radius: 0em;
    }
    &.labeled.icon .${buttonClass}:first-child > .icon {
      border-top-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
      border-bottom-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
    }
    &.labeled.icon .${buttonClass}:last-child > .icon {
      border-top-right-radius: ${borderRadius};
      border-bottom-right-radius: ${borderRadius};
    }
    &.vertical.labeled.icon .${buttonClass}:first-child > .icon {
      border-radius: 0em;
      border-top-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
    }
    &.vertical.labeled.icon .${buttonClass}:last-child > .icon {
      border-radius: 0em;
      border-bottom-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
    }
 
 
 
    &.labeled.icon .${buttonClass} > .icon {
      border-radius: 0em;
    }
    &.labeled.icon .${buttonClass}:first-child > .icon {
      border-top-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
      border-bottom-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
    }
    &.labeled.icon .${buttonClass}:last-child > .icon {
      border-top-right-radius: ${borderRadius};
      border-bottom-right-radius: ${borderRadius};
    }
    &.vertical.labeled.icon .${buttonClass}:first-child > .icon {
      border-radius: 0em;
      border-top-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
    }
    &.vertical.labeled.icon .${buttonClass}:last-child > .icon {
      border-radius: 0em;
      border-bottom-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
    }
 
    ${
      ["mini","tiny","small","medium","large","big","huge","massive"].map((size)=>{
        return `
          &.${size} .${buttonClass},
          &.${size} .or {
            font-size: ${getSize(size)};
          }
        `;
      }).join(" ")
    }
 
    &.compact .${buttonClass} {
      ${compactButton}
    }
    &.compact.icon .${buttonClass} {
      ${compactIconButton}
    }
    &.compact.labeled.icon .${buttonClass} {
      ${compactLabeledIconButton}
    }
 
    /*-------------------
        Basic
    --------------------*/
 
    &.basic {
      box-shadow: none;
      border: none;
      ${'' /* border-radius: ${borderRadius}; */}
    }
 
    &.basic .${buttonClass} {
      ${basicButton(buttonVars)}
      border-radius: 0em;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${basicBorderSize} ${solidifyOpacity(borderColor)} inset;
    }
 
    &.basic:not(.vertical) .${buttonClass} {
      &:first-child {
        border-top-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
        border-bottom-left-radius: ${borderRadius};
      }
      &:last-child {
        border-top-right-radius: ${borderRadius};
        border-bottom-right-radius: ${borderRadius};
      }
    }
 
 
    &.basic .${buttonClass}:hover {
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${unitMath(basicBorderSize,"+","1px")} ${solidifyOpacity(borderColor)} inset;
    }
    &.basic .${buttonClass}:focus {
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${unitMath(basicBorderSize,"+","1px")} ${solidifyOpacity(selectedBorderColor)} inset;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    &.basic .${buttonClass}:active {
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${unitMath(basicBorderSize,"+","2px")} ${solidifyOpacity(borderColor)} inset;
    }
 
    &.basic .${buttonClass}.active {
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${unitMath(basicBorderSize,"+","2px")} ${solidifyOpacity(borderColor)} inset;
    }
 
    &.basic.inverted .${buttonClass} {
      ${basicInvertedButton(buttonVars)}
    }
 
    &.basic {
      border:none;
    }
 
    &.basic .${buttonClass} {
      border: none;
    }
    &.basic:not(.vertical) .${buttonClass}:not(:first-child) {
      margin-left: -1px;
    }
    &.basic.vertical .${buttonClass}:not(:first-child) {
      margin-top: -1px;
    }
 
    /* Basic Group */
    &.basic .${buttonClass} {
      ${'' /* border-left: ${basicGroupBorder}; */}
      ${'' /* box-shadow: none; */}
    }
    ${'' /* &.basic.vertical .${buttonClass} {
      border-left: none;
    } */}
    ${'' /* &.basic.vertical .${buttonClass} {
      border-left-width: 0px;
      ${'' /* border-top: ${basicGroupBorder}; */}
    } */}
    ${'' /* &.basic.vertical .${buttonClass}:first-child {
      border-top-width: 0px;
    } */}
 
    ${'' /* & {
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${basicBorderSize} ${borderColor} inset;
    } */}
    ${'' /* &:hover {
      background: transparent !important;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${unitMath(basicColoredBorderSize,"+","1px")} ${colorHover} inset !important;
      color: ${makeReadable(colorHover)} !important;
    }
    &:focus {
      background: transparent !important;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${unitMath(basicColoredBorderSize,"+","1px")} ${colorFocus} inset !important;
      color: ${makeReadable(colorHover)} !important;
    }
    &.active {
      background: transparent !important;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${unitMath(basicColoredBorderSize,"+","2px")} ${colorActive} inset !important;
      color: ${makeReadable(colorDown)} !important;
    }
    &:active {
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px ${unitMath(basicColoredBorderSize,"+","2px")} ${colorDown} inset !important;
      color: ${makeReadable(colorDown)} !important;
    } */}
 
    /*-------------------
       Inverted
    --------------------*/
 
 
    /* Group */
    &.inverted .${buttonClass} {
      margin: ${invertedGroupButtonOffset};
    }
    &.inverted .${buttonClass}:first-child {
      margin-left: 0em;
    }
    &.inverted.vertical .${buttonClass} {
      margin: ${invertedVerticalGroupButtonOffset};
    }
    &.inverted.vertical .${buttonClass}:first-child {
      margin-top: 0em;
    }
 
    &.fluid {
      width: 100%;
    }
 
    /*-------------------
          Or Buttons
    --------------------*/
 
    & .or {
      position: relative;
      width: ${orGap};
      height: ${orHeight};
      z-index: ${orZIndex};
    }
    & .or:before {
      position: absolute;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: ${circularRadius};
 
      content: "${orText}";
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      background-color: ${orBackgroundColor};
      text-shadow: ${orTextShadow};
 
      margin-top: ${orVerticalOffset};
      margin-left: ${orHorizontalOffset};
 
      width: ${orCircleSize};
      height: ${orCircleSize};
 
      line-height: ${orLineHeight};
      color: ${orTextColor};
 
      font-style: ${orTextStyle};
      font-weight: ${orTextWeight};
 
      box-shadow: ${orBoxShadow};
    }
    & .or[data-text]:before {
      content: attr(data-text);
    }
 
  `;
 
  return {group,button: buttonClass};
});
